<p>Users do have the choice to decline cookies. Most web browsers automatically accept cookies, but people can usually modify their browser setting to decline cookies if they prefer. Should You choose to decline cookies You may be unable to access certain information or parts of Our Website, and some or all of the Services may not work properly. Our advertisers and promoters may also use cookies, over which We have no control.</p>

